          'Setting effective business goals is the cornerstone of sustainable growth for startups and small businesses. Well-defined goals provide direction, motivate teams, and ensure resources are focused on what matters most. This SEO-optimized guide outlines actionable steps to set business goals that drive real growth in 2025, tailored for entrepreneurs aiming to scale efficiently. Whether you’re launching a tech startup or expanding a local business, these strategies will help you achieve meaningful results.',
