        meta_title: '5 Key Performance Metrics Every Small Business Should Track',
        meta_description:
          'Tracking the right key performance metrics (KPIs) is essential for small businesses to measure progress, optimize operations, and drive growth. By focusing on data-driven insights, you can make informed decisions and stay competitive. This SEO-optimized guide highlights five critical KPIs every small business should monitor in 2025, along with actionable steps to track and improve them. Whether you’re running an e-commerce store, a local service, or a tech startup, these metrics will help you achieve sustainable success.',
